This is how to greatest_common_divisor of a and b:
  Remember that x is a
  Remember that y is b
  Do this 1000 times:
    When y is 0, then:
      The answer is x
    End when
    Remember that temp is y
    Remember that y is remainder of x and y
    Remember that x is temp
  End do
  The answer is x
